This is a code Editor

The user can specify what editor they want to use by changing OPTION to what ever preferred editor
Usage:
./workon <file-name>

This will allow you to open <file-name> edit it and save what you added/removed
Then it will utilizes find-error.py to find the error when compiling the edited file and display error if there is any.

User has the option to continue or quit out. 
If chosen to continue the file will be reopened at the line of the error for easy debugging.